<div id="rightsidebar">

<table id="hometable">

  <tr>
	<th colspan="3">Available Countries</th>
  </tr>

	<% for country in @countries %>
	
	<tr>		  
	<td><%= link_to country.country, country %></td>
	 	<% if @logged_in_user && (@logged_in_user.country_id.nil? || @logged_in_user.country_id == country.id) %>
			<td class="editsymbol"><%= link_to '&#916;', edit_country_path(country) %></td>
	  
			<td class="deletesymbol"><%= link_to '&#215;', country, :confirm => 'Are you sure you want to delete country?', :method => :delete %> </td>
		<%end%>
	</tr>
	
	<%end%>
	
	</table>
	
	<% if @logged_in_user && @logged_in_user.country_id.nil? %>
	
		<div id="addcountry"><span style="color:#006000; font-weight:bold;font-size: 16px;">+</span> <%= link_to 'Add a New Country', new_country_path %></div>
	
	<%end%>

</div><!-- rightsidebar -->

<div id="main">
<p>Welcome to the broadband price analyzer! This application lets you explore prices for mobile and fixed broadband service providers in the countries listed on the right. You can compare data in several ways. You may:
<br /><br />
</p>
<h1> Select a Country</h1>
<p>Use the menu on the right side of the page to choose a country/locale in which to compare broadband plans.</p>
<br />

<h1> Choose a Provider</h1>
<p>Select a broadband service provider in your locale.  Depending on the location you choose, you may be offered a variety of options to choose from.</p>
<br />

<h1> Browse</h1>
<p>Browse through important plan features. Browse through plans offered by each provider to find the one that fits you.</p>
<br />

<h1> Compare Plans</h1>
<p>Use the <%= link_to "Compare Plans", url_for(:controller => 'search') %> link to examine the differences between any number of fixed or mobile broadband access plans from any provider.  You will be able to select from different service features. The application will retrieve the relevant information and compare the cost of plans.  This will help you to find the cheapest plan that meets your needs.  A manual that explains key functions in more detail is available here.</p>

</div><!-- main -->

<% if session[:user_id]%>

<div id="logout"><%= link_to "Log Out", url_for(:controller => "user", :action => "log_out")%></div><!-- logout -->

<div id="addnewadmin"><span style="color:#006000; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px;">+</span> <%= link_to("Add a New Administrator", url_for(:action => "new", :controller => 'user'))%></div><!-- addnewadmin -->

<div id="aboutpage">
	<span style="font-weight: bold;">About This Page:</span><br />
	Click a country name to view a profile of that country, including fixed and mobile broadband provider names.  Click the <span style="color: #ffa500; font-weight: bold;">&#916;</span> to change the name of a country, its currency, or the current conversion rate to US Dollars.  To remove a country from the list, click <span style="color: #ff0000; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px;">&#215;</span>.  When you are finished making changes, click the <span style="color: #ff0000;">red</span> link to log out.
